\c 26
\s VaIsraeri, vanogona kurwa, vanoverengwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika shure kwe, kuti Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi nekuna Eriazari mwanakomana Aroni mupristi achiti:
\v 2 Tora uwandu hwese hweungano yese yevana vaIsraeri, kubva pamakore makumi maviri zvichikwira, nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, vese vanogona kuenda kuhondo kwaIsraeri.
\v 3 Zvino Mozisi naEriazari mupristi vakataura navo pamapani aMoabhu paJoridhani paJeriko, vachiti:
\v 4 \add Verengai\add* kubva pamakore makumi maviri zvichikwira; Jehovha sezvakaraira Mozisi nevana vaIsraeri, vakabuda kubva panyika yeEgipita.
\p
\v 5 Rubheni, dangwe raIsraeri, vanakomana vaRubheni: Hanoki, \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yaVaHanoki; kwaParu, mhuri yeVaParu,
\v 6 kwaHezironi mhuri yeVaHezironi; kwaKarimi mhuri yeVaKarimi.
\v 7 Idzi imhuri dzeVaRubheni; nevakaverengwa kwavari vaiva zvuru makumi mana nezvitatu nemazana manomwe nemakumi matatu.
\v 8 Nevanakomana vaParu: Eriabhu;
\v 9 nevanakomana vaEriabhu, Nemueri naDhatani naAbhiramu; Ndivo Dhatani naAbhiramu vakange vakadanwa neungano, vakapikisa Mozisi naAroni paboka raKora, pavakapikisa Jehovha,
\v 10 nyika ndokushamisa muromo wayo, ndokuvamedza pamwe naKora pakafa boka iro; iyo nguva moto yawakaparadza varume mazana maviri nemakumi mashanu, ivo ndokuva chiratidzo.
\v 11 Asi vanakomana VaKora havana kufa.
\p
\v 12 Vanakomana vaSimioni zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaNemueri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaNemueri, kwaJamini mhuri yeVaJamini, kwaJakini mhuri yeVaJakini;
\v 13 kwaZera mhuri yeVaZera; kwaShauri mhuri yeVaShauri.
\v 14 Idzi imhuri dzeVaSimioni, zvuru makumi maviri nezviviri nemazana maviri.
\p
\v 15 Vanakomana vaGadhi zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaZefoni \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaZefoni; kwaHagi mhuri yeVaHagi; kwaShuni mhuri yeVaShuni;
\v 16 kwaZini mhuri yeVaZini; kwaEri mhuri yeVaEri;
\v 17 kwaArodhi mhuri yeVaArodhi; kwaAreri mhuru yeVaAreri.
\v 18 Idzi imhuri dzevanakomana vaGadhi; avo vakaverengwa vavo \add vaiva\add* zvuru makumi mana nemazana mashanu.
\p
\v 19 Vanakomana vaJudha: Eri naOnani; Eri naOnani ndokufira munyika yeKenani.
\v 20 Zvino vanakomana vaJudha zvichitevera mhuri dzavo ndeava: kwaShera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaShera; kwaPerezi mhuri yeVaPerezi; kwaZera \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaZera.
\v 21 Zvino vanakomana VaPerezi ndeava: kwaHezironi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaHezironi; kwaHamuri \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaHamuri.
\v 22 Idzi imhuri dzaJudha; zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi manomwe nezvitanhatu nemazana mashanu.
\p
\v 23 Vanakomana vaIsaskari zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: Tora \add we\add*mhuri yeVaTora; kwaPuwa \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaPuwa;
\v 24 kwaJashubhi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaJashubhi, kwaShimironi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yeVaShimironi.
\v 25 Idzi imhuri dzaIsaskari zvichienderana nevakaverengwa vavo; zvuru makumi matanhatu nezvina nemazana matatu.
\p
\v 26 Vanakomana vaZebhuruni zvichitevera mhuri dzavo: kwaSeredhi \add kwakabva\add* mhuri yaVaSeredhi; naEroni, kwakabva mhuri yaVaEroni; naJahareeri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaJahareeri.
\v 27 Ndidzo mhuri dzeVaZebhuruni; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi matanhatu namazana mashanu.
\p
\v 28 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaJosefa, nemhuri dzavo: Manase naEfuremu.
\v 29 Ndivo vanakomana vaManase: Makiri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaMakiri; Makiri wakabereka Giriyadhi; kunaGiriyadhi kwakabva mhuri yaVaGiriyadhi.
\v 30 Ndivo vanakomana vaGiriyadhi: Jezeri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaJezeri; naHereki, kwakabva mhuri yaVaHereki;
\v 31 naAsirieri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaAsirieri; naShekemu, kwakabva mhuri yaVaShekemu;
\v 32 naShemidha, kwakabva mhuri yaVaShemidha; naHeferi, kwakabva mhuri yaVaHeferi.
\p
\v 33 Asi Zerofehadhi, mwanakomana waHeferi, akange asina vanakomana, asi vanasikana chete; mazita avanasikana vaZerofehadhi aiva Makira, naNowa, naHogira, naMirika, naTiriza.
\v 34 Ndidzo mhuri dzaManase; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi mashanu nezviviri namazana manomwe.
\p
\v 35 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaEfuremu, nemhuri dzavo: Shutera, kwakabva mhuri yaVaShutera; naBhekeri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaBhekeri, naTahani, kwakabva mhuri yaVaTahani.
\v 36 Ndivo vanakomana vaShutera: Erani, kwakabva mhuri yaVaErani.
\p
\v 37 Ndidzo mhuri dzavanakomana vaEfuremu; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi matatu nezviviri, namazana mashanu. Ndivo vanakomana vaJosefa, nemhuri dzavo.
\p
\v 38 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaBhenjamini, nemhuri dzavo: Bhera, kwakabva mhuri yaVaBhera; naAshibheri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaAshibheri; naAhirami, kwakabva mhuri yaVaAhirami;
\v 39 naShefufami, kwakabva mhuri yaVaShufami; naHufami, kwakabva mhuri yaVaHufami.
\v 40 Ndivo vanakomana vaBhera: Aridhi naNamani; kuna Aridhi kwakabva mhuri yaVaAridhi; naNamani, kwakabva mhuri yaVaNamani.
\v 41 Ndivo vanakomana vaBhenjamini, nemhuri dzavo; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi mana nezvishanu namazana matanhatu.
\p
\v 42 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaDhani, nemhuri dzavo: Shuhami, kwakabva mhuri yaVaShuhami. Ndivo vemhuri dzaDhani, nedzimba dzavo.
\v 43 Mhuri dzese dzavaShuhami, vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi matanhatu nezvina namazana mana.
\p
\v 44 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaAsheri, nemhuri dzavo: Jimina, kwakabva mhuri yaVaJimina; naIshivhi, kwakabva mhuri yaVaIshivhi; naBheria, kwakabva mhuri yaVaBheria.
\v 45 Ndivo vanakomana vaBheria: Hebheri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaHebheri; naMakieri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaMakieri.
\v 46 Zita romwanasikana waAsheri rakange riri Sera.
\v 47 Ndidzo mhuri dzaAsheri; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi mashanu nezvitanhatu namazana mana.
\p
\v 48 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaNafutari, nemhuri dzavo: Jazeeri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaJazeri; naGuni, kwakabva mhuri yaVaGuni;
\v 49 naJezeri, kwakabva mhuri yaVaJezeri; naShiremi, kwakabva mhuri yaVaShiremi.
\v 50 Ndidzo mhuri dzaNafutari, nemhuri dzavo; vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi mana nezvishanu namazana mana.
\p
\v 51 Ndivo vakaverengwa kuvana vaIsraeri, vakasvika zvuru zvina mazana matanhatu nechiuru chimwe namazana manomwe namakumi matatu.
\p
\v 52 Jehovha akataura naMozisi, akati:
\v 53 Nyika inofanira kugoverwa pakati paivava, ive nhaka yavo, vachiverengwa namazita avo.
\v 54 Vazhinji unofanira kuvapa nhaka zhinji; vashoma unofanira kuvapa nhaka shoma; umwe neumwe unofanira kupiwa sezvavakaverengwa.
\v 55 Kunyange zvakadaro nyika inofanira kugoverwa nemijenya; vachapiwa nhaka namazita amarudzi amadzibaba avo.
\v 56 Nhaka yavo inofanira kugoverwa nemijenya kana vari vazhinji kana vari vashoma.
\p
\v 57 Zvino ndivo vakaverengwa kuVaRevhi, nemhuri dzavo: Gerishoni, kwakabva mhuri yaVaGerishoni; Kohati, kwakabva mhuri yaVaKohati; Merari, kwakabva mhuri yaVaMerari.
\v 58 Ndidzo mhuri dzaVaRevhi: Mhuri yaVaRibhini, nemhuri yaVaHebhuroni, nemhuri yaVaMari, nemhuri yaVaMushi, nemhuri yaVaKora. Kohati akabereka Amuramu.
\v 59 Zita romukadzi waAmuramu rakange riri Jokebhedhi, mwanasikana waRevhi, wakaberekerwa Revhi paEgipita; ndiye wakaberekera Amuramu, Aroni, naMozisi, naMiriami, hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 60 Aroni akaberekerwa Nadhabhi, naAbhihu, naEriazari, naItamari.
\v 61 Nadhabhi naAbhihu vakafa, nguva yavakauisa moto usina kufanira pamberi paJehovha.
\v 62 Vakaverengwa kwavari vakasvika zvuru zvina makumi maviri nezvitatu, murume umwe neumwe kubva mwanakomana wemwedzi umwe zvichikwira; nokuti havana kuverengwa pakati pavana vaIsraeri, nokuti havana kupiwa nhaka pakati pavana vaIsraeri.
\p
\v 63 Ndivo vakaverengwa naMozisi naEriazari mupristi, vakaverenga vana vaIsraeri pamapani aMoabhu, paJoridhani paJeriko.
\v 64 Asi pakati pavo kwakange kusina murume umwe wavaya vakaverengwa naMozisi naAroni, vakange vaverenga vana vaIsraeri murenje reSinai.
\v 65 Nokuti Jehovha akange ati napamusoro pavo: Zvirokwazvo vachafira murenje. Hakuna umwe wavo akange asara, asi Karebhu, mwanakomana waJefune, naJoshua, mwanakomana waNuni.
